# Visual Design Exploration : duolingo Redesign 

## About this Project
This is an early visual design concept for a mobila application, focusing on restructuting the user interface of a well-known education app (Duolingo). The goal was to experiment with scree layouts and user flow simplification.

## Status 
Initial Design Mockup Phase 1 (work in progress)
